    <title>HPP专用测试文章</title>
    <url>/2021/02/06/1/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>最近博主上手了<a href="https://github.com/ChenYFan">@ChenYFan</a>开发的hexo后台系统<a href="https://github.com/HexoPlusPlus/HexoPlusPlus">HexoPlusPlus</a>，<del>然后成为了HPP测试版的小白鼠</del></p>
<p>又不想在测试过程中拿去修改其他的文章，所以单开一页专门测试</p>
<p>以下为日常测试内容</p>
<hr>
<h2 id="试一试新建"><a href="#试一试新建" class="headerlink" title="试一试新建"></a>试一试新建</h2><h2 id="试一试更改"><a href="#试一试更改" class="headerlink" title="试一试更改"></a>试一试更改</h2><h2 id="试一试图片上传"><a href="#试一试图片上传" class="headerlink" title="试一试图片上传"></a>试一试图片上传</h2><p><img src="https://cdn1.tianli0.top/gh/2X-ercha/picture-bed@master/1612602820000.png"></p>
<h2 id="试一试手机端"><a href="#试一试手机端" class="headerlink" title="试一试手机端"></a>试一试手机端</h2><p>输入法：中文&#x2F;English</p>
<h2 id="试一试表情"><a href="#试一试表情" class="headerlink" title="试一试表情"></a>试一试表情</h2><p><img src="https://cdn1.tianli0.top/gh/Dreamy-TZK/iemotion-pic@latest/img/QQ/0.gif"><img src="https://cdn1.tianli0.top/gh/Dreamy-TZK/iemotion-pic@latest/img/bilibili_tv_gif/doge.gif"><img src="https://cdn1.tianli0.top/gh/2x-ercha/twikoo-magic/image/bilibili2233/[2233%E5%A8%98_%E5%8D%96%E8%90%8C].png"><img src="https://cdn1.tianli0.top/gh/2x-ercha/twikoo-magic/image/Menhera-chan/1.jpg"><img src="https://cdn1.tianli0.top/gh/2x-ercha/twikoo-magic/image/Tsuri-me-ju_mimi/10753776_key@2x.png"><img src="https://cdn1.tianli0.top/gh/2x-ercha/twikoo-magic/image/Mafumafu/199749454.png"><img src="https://cdn1.tianli0.top/gh/2x-ercha/twikoo-magic/image/Snow-Miku/3583066@2x.png"><img src="https://cdn1.tianli0.top/gh/2x-ercha/twikoo-magic/image/Sweetie-Bunny/12311678.png"><img src="https://cdn1.tianli0.top/gh/2x-ercha/twikoo-magic/image/aodamiao/01.gif"><img src="https://cdn1.tianli0.top/gh/2x-ercha/twikoo-magic/image/Heybox/expression_cube.png"><img src="https://cdn1.tianli0.top/gh/2x-ercha/twikoo-magic/image/baitian/file_6574832.webp"><img src="https://cdn1.tianli0.top/gh/2x-ercha/twikoo-magic/image/weisuomeng/1.jpg"><img src="https://cdn1.tianli0.top/gh/Dreamy-TZK/iemotion-pic@latest/img/%E7%BD%97%E5%B0%8F%E9%BB%91/%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD%E5%91%80.png"><img src="https://cdn1.tianli0.top/gh/Dreamy-TZK/iemotion-pic@latest/img/%E9%82%A3%E5%85%94/%E3%80%82%E3%80%82%E3%80%82.png"></p>
<hr>
<p><a href="mailto:&#72;&#101;&#120;&#x6f;&#80;&#108;&#x75;&#x73;&#x50;&#x6c;&#x75;&#x73;&#64;&#x31;&#46;&#x30;&#46;&#55;">&#72;&#101;&#120;&#x6f;&#80;&#108;&#x75;&#x73;&#x50;&#x6c;&#x75;&#x73;&#64;&#x31;&#46;&#x30;&#46;&#55;</a>测试结束，没有bug</p>
